description: Lists all subscriptions created in an Amazon Q Business application.

parameters.name: applicationId
parameters.description: The identifier of the Amazon Q Business application linked to the subscription.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: If the response is truncated, Amazon Q Business returns this token. You can use this token in a subsequent request to retrieve the next set of subscriptions.

nested_items.name: subscriptions
nested_items.description: An array of summary information on the subscriptions configured for an Amazon Q Business application.

nested_items.name: subscriptionId
nested_items.description: The identifier of the Amazon Q Business subscription to be updated.

nested_items.name: subscriptionArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Amazon Q Business subscription that was updated.

nested_items.name: principal
nested_items.description: The IAM Identity Center UserId or GroupId of a user or group in the IAM Identity Center instance connected to the Amazon Q Business application.

nested_items.name: user
nested_items.description: The identifier of a user in the IAM Identity Center instance connected to the Amazon Q Business application.

nested_items.name: group
nested_items.description: The identifier of a group in the IAM Identity Center instance connected to the Amazon Q Business application.

nested_items.name: currentSubscription
nested_items.description: The type of your current Amazon Q Business subscription.

nested_items.name: type
nested_items.description: The type of an Amazon Q Business subscription.

nested_items.name: nextSubscription
nested_items.description: The type of the Amazon Q Business subscription for the next month.

nested_items.name: type
nested_items.description: The type of an Amazon Q Business subscription.
